---
/**
 * Sección negra:
 * - Arriba: CEREMONIA / VENUE + fotos
 * - Abajo: rosas, mesas de regalo y foto “save the date”
 */
---

<section class="bg-black text-white w-full overflow-hidden py-20 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24">
  
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col gap-24">

    <article class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center">
      
      <div class="md:col-span-7 flex flex-col w-full">
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-serif tracking-widest text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          CEREMONIA<br/>RELIGIOSA
        </h2>

        <hr class="border-t border-gray-600 w-full mb-6" />

        <div class="flex flex-row justify-between items-start text-lg md:text-xl font-light tracking-wide uppercase">
          
          <div class="flex flex-col text-left">
            <span class="font-bold">03:00</span>
            <span>PM</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col text-right">
            <span class="font-bold">Templo de Santo</span>
            <span>Domingo</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="border-t border-gray-600 w-full mt-6" />
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-5 w-full flex justify-center md:justify-end mt-8 md:mt-0">
        <div class="w-full max-w-sm aspect-[4/5] bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 overflow-hidden relative shadow-2xl">
          <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/1SFigC63c67MFYZf8">
          <img   
            src="/images/ceremonia-templo.png"
            alt="Templo de Santo Domingo" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700 ease-in-out"
          />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>


    <article class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center">
      
      <div class="md:col-span-7 flex flex-col w-full">
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-serif tracking-widest text-white mb-6">
          VENUE
        </h2>

        <hr class="border-t border-gray-600 w-full mb-6" />

        <div class="flex flex-row justify-between items-start text-lg md:text-xl font-light tracking-wide uppercase">
          
          <div class="flex flex-col text-left">
            <span class="font-bold">05:00</span>
            <span>PM</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col text-right">
            <span class="font-bold">Hacienda Viñedo</span>
            <span>La Solariega</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 normal-case mt-1">Acceso 2</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="border-t border-gray-600 w-full mt-6" />
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-5 w-full flex justify-center md:justify-end mt-8 md:mt-0">
        <div class="w-full max-w-sm aspect-[4/5] bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 overflow-hidden relative shadow-2xl">
          <a
          href="https://waze.com/ul/h9g8ss7vpn">
          <img 
            src="/images/venue-solariega.png"" 
            alt="Hacienda Viñedo La Solariega" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700 ease-in-out"
          />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

  </div>


    <!-- PARTE INFERIOR: ROSAS + REGALOS + FOTO -->
    <div
      class="mt-16 pt-10 border-t border-white/20 flex flex-col gap-10 lg:flex-row lg:items-center"
    >
     <!-- Rosas --> 
      <div class="@container lg:w-1/3 flex justify-center lg:justify-start"> 
        <img src="/images/rosas.png" 
        alt="Rosas" 
        class="max-h-[380px] w-auto @sm:max-h-[240px] @md:max-h-[300px] @lg:max-h-[340px] @xl:max-h-[380px]" /> 
      </div>

      <!-- Texto de regalos -->
      <div
        class="lg:w-1/3 text-center lg:text-left space-y-5 max-w-md mx-auto lg:mx-0"
      >
        <p
          class=" [font-family:'ShelleyScript'] text-[32px] sm:text-[40px] md:text-[52px] lg:text-[64px] xl:text-[76.3px] leading-snug"
        >
          Tu presencia hará este día aún más especial !
        </p>

        <p class="[font-family:'Optima'] text-sm md:text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed">
          Si deseas hacernos un detalle, puedes apoyarnos a través de
          nuestra mesa de regalos o con una aportación para nuestro
          futuro juntos.
        </p>

        <p class="[font-family:'Optima'] text-sm md:text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed">
          Liverpool - Número de evento: 51844655<br />
          SEARS - Mesa # 219515
        </p>

        <p class="[font-family:'Optima'] text-sm md:text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          ¡Gracias por ser parte de este momento!
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Foto save the date -->
      <div class="lg:w-1/3 flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
        <img
          src="/images/regalos-save-the-date.png"
          alt="Foto save the date"
          class="w-76 sm:w-68 lg:w-82 object-cover shadow-lg"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  
</section>
